---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
---

<Layout title="Shara Mae – AI & Cloud Engineer">
  <Header />

    <main class="shell main">
    <!-- Centered intro panel -->
    <section class="intro-wrapper">
      <div class="intro-panel">
        <h2>AI &amp; Cloud Engineer for enterprise workloads.</h2>

        <p class="intro-text">
          I design and build production-ready solutions across AI automation, backend APIs,
          Microsoft 365 platforms, and full-stack experiences. Over 6 years I’ve worked with
          global organisations in healthcare, modern workplace, and XR to ship secure,
          maintainable systems on Azure.
        </p>

        <div class="intro-tags">
          <span>AI Engineering</span>
          <span>Backend APIs</span>
          <span>Microsoft 365 &amp; Copilot</span>
          <span>Full-Stack &amp; XR</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Role cards -->
    <section class="grid">
      <article class="card">
        <h3>AI Engineer</h3>
        <p>
          Building intelligent pipelines with Azure OpenAI, AI Search, document processing,
          and agent-based orchestration to automate complex workflows.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Healthcare eFax automation using LLMs and vector search</li>
          <li>Document classification and extraction on Azure</li>
          <li>Agent-driven orchestration for laptop refresh initiatives</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h3>Backend Engineer</h3>
        <p>
          Designing and implementing APIs, integration layers, and data services with
          observability and testing built-in.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Python FastAPI services with pytest test suites</li>
          <li>PostgreSQL and Azure Blob Storage for resilient data</li>
          <li>Deployments via Azure Functions and App Service</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h3>Microsoft 365 &amp; Automation</h3>
        <p>
          Leveraging Copilot Studio, Power Automate, SharePoint, and PVA to streamline
          enterprise processes and knowledge access.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Copilot Studio agents integrated with ServiceNow flows</li>
          <li>SharePoint-based dashboards and automation tools</li>
          <li>Notification engines and migration initiatives</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h3>Full-Stack &amp; XR</h3>
        <p>
          Delivering immersive and modern experiences from user interface through to
          cloud services.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Unity-based XR projects for retail and healthcare</li>
          <li>Metaverse POCs for environmental sustainability</li>
          <li>SharePoint &amp; Teams customisations for modern workplace</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </section>
  </main>

</Layout>

<style>
  .main {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }



  .grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
  }

  .card {
	background: linear-gradient(
		180deg,
		rgba(16, 19, 37, 0.98),
		rgba(8, 10, 26, 0.95)
	);
	border-radius: 1rem;
	padding: 1.7rem;
	border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.28);
	transition: border-color 0.25s ease, transform 0.25s ease,
		box-shadow 0.25s ease;
	}

	.card:hover {
	border-color: rgba(236, 95, 169, 0.55);
	box-shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(5, 6, 23, 0.9);
	transform: translateY(-2px);
	}

  .card h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .card p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .card ul {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  /* Centers the whole intro section in the page */
	.intro-wrapper {
	display: flex;
	justify-content: center;
	margin: 3rem 0 3.5rem;
	}

	/* The panel itself */
	.intro-panel {
	max-width: 780px;
	width: 100%;
	background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #151833 0%, #050617 80%);
	border-radius: 1.1rem;
	padding: 2rem 2.25rem;
	text-align: center;
	border: 1px solid rgba(236, 95, 169, 0.5);
	box-shadow:
		0 0 0 1px rgba(236, 95, 169, 0.15),
		0 22px 55px rgba(5, 6, 23, 0.95);
	}

	/* Text */
	.intro-text {
	color: var(--text-muted);
	line-height: 1.6;
	margin: 0.75rem 0 1.4rem;
	}

	/* Tags */
	.intro-tags {
	display: flex;
	flex-wrap: wrap;
	gap: 0.5rem;
	justify-content: center;
	}

	.intro-tags span {
	padding: 0.4rem 0.95rem;
	border-radius: 999px;
	font-size: 0.76rem;
	border: 1px solid rgba(236, 95, 169, 0.45);
	background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
	color: #f9fafb;
	letter-spacing: 0.03em;
	}

</style>
